<section class="sec" style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="post-wrap post-body reveal">
<h2>Explainer Videos That Drive Sales and Engagement</h2> <p>Explainer videos increase product sales and customer engagement because they simplify complex offerings into a clear, visual story that builds trust and drives action fast. According to Wyzowl, 96% of people have watched an explainer video to learn more about a product or service, and 89% say a video convinced them to make a purchase — turning interest into conversions at every stage of the funnel.</p> <h3>Why Explainer Videos Are Critical for Product Marketing</h3> <p><a href={p("services/how-to-video")}>Explainer videos</a> do more than educate — they build trust and accelerate decision-making. Key benefits include:</p> <ul> <li><strong>Instantly capturing attention:</strong> video content engages customers within seconds.</li> <li><strong>Simplifying complex ideas:</strong> explainers break down intricate product details into easy-to-understand visuals.</li> <li><strong>Driving action:</strong> a strong call to action leads to higher conversion rates, pushing viewers closer to a purchase.</li> </ul> <h3>Simplifying Complex Products Through Visual Storytelling</h3> <p>Explainer videos use visual storytelling to make complex products or services easy to understand. By combining animation, visuals, and narration, they clearly highlight key features and benefits — ideal for technical, financial, or healthcare products. According to Insivia, viewers retain 95% of a message when they watch it in a video, compared to just 10% when reading text. A SaaS company, for example, could use an explainer video to show how its product streamlines workflows and improves data accuracy.</p> <h3>Increasing Engagement and Holding Attention</h3> <p>With attention spans as short as 8 seconds on average (Microsoft research), explainer videos capture and hold attention longer than traditional content. A concise, entertaining, and visually appealing format keeps viewers engaged and reduces bounce rates — and engaging videos are more likely to be shared on social media, increasing brand visibility.</p> <h3>Driving Sales with Strong Calls to Action</h3> <p>A well-crafted call to action directs viewers to the next step — signing up for a free trial, scheduling a demo, or making a purchase. Wyzowl reports that 84% of people have been convinced to buy a product or service after watching a video, tying explainer videos directly to purchasing decisions.</p> <h3>Building Trust and Customer Confidence</h3> <p>Explainer videos foster transparency and clarity, helping potential customers feel confident in their decision. Adding <a href={p("services/product-video")}>customer testimonials</a>, product demonstrations, or data-backed results further boosts credibility, presenting real-world applications that strengthen the relationship with your audience.</p> <h3>Expanding Reach with Multi-Channel Distribution</h3> <p>Explainer videos are versatile and can be shared across multiple platforms:</p> <ul> <li><strong>Product pages:</strong> embedding videos boosts SEO and increases the chances of conversion.</li> <li><strong>Email campaigns:</strong> including video increases engagement and click-through rates.</li> <li><strong>Social media:</strong> LinkedIn, Facebook, and Instagram allow for easy sharing and increased exposure.</li> </ul> <p>Forrester found that video content is 50 times more likely to drive organic search results than text, making explainer videos valuable for SEO as well as conversion.</p> <h3>Measuring Success</h3> <p>To ensure explainer videos meet business goals, track view counts, engagement (watch time, likes, comments, shares), click-through rates, and conversion rates — then use these metrics to refine future campaigns.</p> <p>As customer behavior continues to favor video content, explainer videos remain a cornerstone of any successful marketing strategy. For more, see our guide to <a href={p("blog/maximizing-customer-conversion-with-explainer-videos-a-strategic-guide")}>maximizing conversion with explainer videos</a> or how brands <a href={p("blog/how-brands-simplify-complex-products-with-explainer-videos")}>simplify complex products with explainer videos</a>.</p> <p>Viven creates custom explainer videos that simplify your message, engage your audience, and drive conversions. <a href={p("contact")}>Get started with Viven</a> to enhance your product marketing strategy.</p>
    </div>
